EN: We need to install steps on the staircase.

ZH: 这个公园的阶梯非常陡峭。
EN: The stairs in this park are very steep.

ZH: 每节楼梯上有五个阶梯。
EN: There are five steps on each staircase.

ZH: 他摔倒在了楼梯的第一级阶梯上。
EN: He fell on the first step of the staircase.

ZH: 请小心走楼梯的每个阶梯。
EN: Please be careful with each step on the staircase.

ZH: 她迈着坚定的步伐走上阶梯。
EN: She walked up the stairs with determined steps.

