EN: This staircase is made of wooden boards.

ZH: 他沿着阶梯小心地下楼。
EN: He carefully descended the stairs.

ZH: 我们在楼梯上放了一些装饰性的阶梯垫。
EN: We put some decorative step mats on the stairs.

