EN: Please do not bump into the edge of the steps.

ZH: 在楼梯上打滑非常危险。
EN: It is very dangerous to slip on the stairs.

ZH: 那个女孩跳过了两个阶梯。
EN: The girl skipped two steps on the staircase.

ZH: 这个建筑的阶梯设计非常独特。
EN: The staircase design of this building is very unique.

ZH: 他们沿着阶梯快速奔跑。
EN: They ran quickly along the steps of the staircase.

ZH: 我们需要清洁每个阶梯上的灰尘。
EN: We need to clean the dust on each step of the staircase.

ZH: 别把东西遗落在阶梯上。
EN: Don't leave anything on the steps of the staircase.

ZH: 我们需要修复这段破损的阶梯。
EN: We need to repair this damaged step of the staircase.

ZH: 他一下子跳下了整个阶梯。
EN: He jumped down the entire flight of steps.

ZH: 她一步一步地爬上了阶梯。
